title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Airbus H135 helicopter - Collective position unsafe
description:
Probably you have seen the following message when flying the Airbus H134 "collective position unsafe"
In this how to I will show you what is causing the warning "collective position unsafe" and how to resolve it.

If you also want to give the helicopter a try download the  Airbus H135 from the site below:
